### Admin login (run first — copies token below)
# @name adminLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/admin/login
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "email": "{{adminEmail}}",
  "password": "{{adminPassword}}"
}

###

@adminToken = {{adminLogin.response.body.accessToken}}

### List all tools (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/tools
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### List tools — query
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/tools?category=Media&featured=true
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get tool by slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/tools/image-compressor
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Create tool
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/tools
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "slug": "demo-tool",
  "name": "Demo Tool",
  "tagline": "For API testing",
  "description": "Temporary tool created via REST Client for smoke tests.",
  "category": "Formatting",
  "icon": "wrench",
  "accent": "violet",
  "status": "soon",
  "keywords": ["demo", "test"],
  "featured": false
}

###

### Update tool status → ready
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/tools/qr-generator
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "status": "ready",
  "featured": true
}

###

### Update tool (partial)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/tools/demo-tool
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "tagline": "Updated tagline from admin API"
}

###

### Delete tool
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/tools/demo-tool
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Admin categories list
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json
